title: Suspicious DNS TXT Record Queries
id: 3c1e90aa-9aa2-4df3-a129-923f001ee7c9
status: experimental
description: Detects a high volume of DNS queries seeking TXT records, which is a common pattern for DNS tunneling or Command and Control communication.
author: Detection Engineer Specialist
date: 2026/06/28
tags:
    - attack.command_and_control
    - attack.t1071.004
logsource:
    product: windows
    service: dns-client
detection:
    selection:
        QueryType: 16 # Type TXT
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Legitimate enterprise applications utilizing DNS TXT verification lookups (e.g., Office 365 activation, SPF/DKIM verification checks).
level: medium